{"tid":422526,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"齊來認識伊斯蘭教","createTime":"2017-10-03T06:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T04:41:30.000Z","uid":20816,"like":12,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b472b265740cd44f479d01cb1d42bfdc507cf5","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"回人相信耶和華神有見於之前嘅先知/使者留下的經典都被篡改內容<br />\n決定親自寫本經文（中譯可蘭經或古蘭經）<br />\n然後搵個最初出左名誠實嘅文盲穆罕默德黎讀俾世人聽<br />\n就係貪佢老實唔會加鹽加醋同唔識加鹽加醋<br />\n如果比喻耶和華神做玉皇大帝<br />\n穆罕默德就係負責讀「皇帝召曰」嗰條友<br />\n按此推論，穆罕默德的個人習慣、對社會制度、政治制度、做人處世態度甚至對可/古蘭經的解釋都完全無參考價值<br />\n但回人在穆罕默德死後卻將他的言行製成hadith(中譯聖訓）<br />\n雖然有部份清醒少少嘅回人知道hadith有真有假<br />\n但現世代伊斯蘭法據講有大部份係根據hadith寫成甚至有些係違反可/古蘭經（此説有待考證）"},{"pid":"6a8999bdc20f6103f3b79225b5a3be229578b6e6","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"可/古蘭經與聖經的主要分別<br />\n<br />\n1.阿當未食禁果時並非不能分辨善惡，而係比天使們更叻，好多天使們唔識嘅阿當都識<br />\n2.阿當夏娃在伊甸園時係有衫著，食咗禁果先俾惡魔除晒d衫<br />\n3.羅得並沒有和女兒亂倫<br />\n4.阿伯拉罕獻上的是大兒子以實馬利<br />\n5.耶穌不是耶和華神的兒子（但同樣相信瑪利亞無俾人插入射精下懷有耶穌）<br />\n6.耶穌都係叫人守番以前班先知/使者教導人類要守嘅規則<br />\n7.耶穌沒有被釘死在十字架上"},{"pid":"6e529c323c7db57d1284e2043c350ee752364d08","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教的五功（唸經、齋戒、禮拜、天課、朝聖）其實係over simplified咗呢個宗教對信徒嘅要求<br />\n如果只需要守五功，即係偷呃拐騙黃賭毒強姦非禮樣樣做齊都無問題<br />\n淨係講番性愛先，可/古蘭經規定只可以與妻子（們）和女奴隸性交<br />\n與這些女人以外嘅女人做愛都係違反可/古蘭經<br />\n有基督徒同極端組織就認為喺街見到嘅女異教徒同女不信者=回人的女奴隸<br />\n所以「根據」可/古蘭經「教導」係可以周街強姦非禮女異教徒和女不信者<br />\n至於此説能否成立就要你自己判斷下"},{"pid":"47eaaeae6c32f46c307ec358e8877118000d043e","tid":422526,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"大家信同一個神 點解個故仔黎到伊斯蘭世界會改哂?"},{"pid":"b18dbc24331e6fef76ae228f52236d8a7e4a647b","tid":422526,"uid":143652,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，信有神嘅人都係戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"2b41056731ab7d919d64d5254fd47babdeee9369","tid":422526,"uid":3668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"CANCER"},{"pid":"3ef4cb0af561ed9dac5375abc9be753fd2cd063a","tid":422526,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"認真POST 留名"},{"pid":"8fb21518972144562646c94244f4a63b101e66ab","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家信同一個神 點解個故仔黎到伊斯蘭世界會改哂?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢點我就唔知<br />\n不過佢地改嘅地方好多都係反耶人士「攻擊」聖經嘅地方<br />\n唔排除係基督徒傳教時遇到自己都解釋唔到嘅章節<br />\n於是班異端「寫」可/古蘭經嘅時候就改動內容避開呢d「攻擊」<br />\n另外問過一名基督徒<br />\n佢話可/古蘭經因為要取悅自稱係以實馬利後代嘅阿拉伯人所以更改阿伯拉罕獻上二兒子以撒故事的主人翁<br />\n不過睇番聖經創世紀22:2<br />\n「神說、你帶着你的兒子、就是你獨生的兒子、你所愛的以撒、往摩利亞地去、在我所要指示你的山上、把他獻為燔祭。」<br />\n基督徒解釋因為耶和華神不承認以實馬利，所以獨生的兒子係解以撒<br />\n但前幾段「劇情」明明係耶和華神叫阿伯拉罕娶個婢女然後生仔<br />\n轉過頭卻又唔認數<br />\n我覺得呢個故事合理嘅解釋係以撒未出生前阿伯拉罕帶佢當時獨生的兒子以實馬利上山獻祭<br />\n用番耶撚嘅陰謀論角度<br />\n因為聖經要取悅自稱係以撒後代嘅猶太人所以更改故事的主人翁做以撒"},{"pid":"d5b38d57753bffb477e167c289a851ae06fd3a2a","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句，信有神嘅人都係戇鳩鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n科學證明唔到有無神<br />\n斷言無神亦唔係一個信科學嘅態度"},{"pid":"461cbe0fc40a98d1d94e3d613b0424c33220f5e6","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CANCER</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9b10452234b380516a3d26177b684bcda57ee8","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真POST 留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfd7a01f81506932420f9b27d1906ced111d0d9","tid":422526,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"雖然我都係無神論者不過都想知道點解咁多人信依啲嘢"},{"pid":"a7a72486aa703c9d12fbff53803d0a175e451808","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我都係無神論者不過都想知道點解咁多人信依啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信伊斯蘭教好多係「世襲」<br />\n即係老豆老母信，仔女就跟住信"},{"pid":"878333aef81a503b12b2ac1a038455ce802c04c9","tid":422526,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"係咩原因令伊斯蘭教越發越勁，例如好似基督教咁做左羅馬國教，唐三藏取大乘佛法？"},{"pid":"9c56bc6879bd0cf46dfd26414411d84a42fa6682","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咩原因令伊斯蘭教越發越勁，例如好似基督教咁做左羅馬國教，唐三藏取大乘佛法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中世紀就勁<br />\n現代衰落啦<br />\n至於基督徒話伊斯蘭用武力傳教<br />\n咁都要基督徒唔夠打先得<br />\n而伊斯蘭教徒在中世紀點解咁好打<br />\n就真係要深入研究先答到你<br />\n<br />\n可是我知道喺中世紀時伊斯蘭教徒控制嘅地方<br />\n異教徒同不信者只需要交多d稅<br />\n無記載話搞宗教審判所之類<br />\n相比當時歐洲，確實吸引到好多人材到中東<br />\n有巴打曾經提出佢睇過資料話中世紀耶路撒冷嘅猶太人長期被基督徒迫害<br />\n所以求回人打救佢<br />\n不過我google唔到有關資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_Golden_Age\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIslamic_Golden_Age&d=ziEEZpoG8a6kV4yLpptPHpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=29e64289\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_Golden_Age</a><br />\n<br />\n另外我個人認為可/古蘭經係基督教異端寫嘅亦都解答左不少反耶有神論者疑問<br />\n所以一推出市面<br />\n就迅即得到長期被迫害嘅異端同反耶有神論者支持<br />\n所以信徒可能因此迅速增長"},{"pid":"30c61698d506a8b0fde1a528d7f8513be5718bce","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"Google 到少少資料<br />\n可以參考下<br />\n<br />\nWhy did Islam spread so quickly in the beginning?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Why-did-Islam-spread-so-quickly-in-the-beginning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhy-did-Islam-spread-so-quickly-in-the-beginning&d=ziEEZpoG8a6kV4yLpptPHpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=035e3653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/Why-did-Islam-spread-so-quickly-in-the-beginning</a>"},{"pid":"b1d84a1a470e8769747f01a66b0cfaa3c3e88692","tid":422526,"uid":112845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句，信有神嘅人都係戇鳩鳩</blockquote><br />\n唔會得罪,事實嚟,信有神嘅人真係戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"3094640c7b54696c24ad072fc5c4c5b3812f094d","tid":422526,"uid":32486,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"雖然好憎伊斯蘭教<br />\n但又真係搵唔到位入佢<br />\n<br />\n如果話佢係假先知 <br />\n咁耶穌 摩西 亞伯拉罕等依啲先知又如何確定係真<br />\n<br />\n你話可蘭經教義野蠻<br />\n咁舊約聖經都係野蠻<br />\n新約都係重男輕女<br />\n只係冇講得咁極端<br />\n同一夫一妻較符合現代人口味<br />\n<br />\n如果否定伊斯蘭咁基督教都有啲站唔住腳<br />\n利申：憎伊斯蘭 但尊重基督教"},{"pid":"456b9e73c12a23ef18eb34fc576ce4f0c49fd039","tid":422526,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然好憎伊斯蘭教<br />\n但又真係搵唔到位入佢<br />\n<br />\n如果話佢係假先知 <br />\n咁耶穌 摩西 亞伯拉罕等依啲先知又如何確定係真<br />\n<br />\n你話可蘭經教義野蠻<br />\n咁舊約聖經都係野蠻<br />\n新約都係重男輕女<br />\n只係冇講得咁極端<br />\n同一夫一妻較符合現代人口味<br />\n<br />\n如果否定伊斯蘭咁基督教都有啲站唔住腳<br />\n利申：憎伊斯蘭 但尊重基督教</blockquote><br />\n宗教撚圍爐小圈子唔影響其他人真係有鳩你，但伊斯蘭教連非教徒都影響埋就過左火，耶撚都識世俗化唔會強迫非教徒遵守教義"},{"pid":"820279aa3afa54e25a7bf157d417646d7c32ec06","tid":422526,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咩原因令伊斯蘭教越發越勁，例如好似基督教咁做左羅馬國教，唐三藏取大乘佛法？</blockquote><br />\n東羅馬同薩珊波斯打左廿幾年仗殘晒<br />\n咁佢地咪冷手執個熱煎堆"},{"pid":"8180d7a04c6908da46ddb4b2bdf600cda22e8ccb","tid":422526,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咩原因令伊斯蘭教越發越勁，例如好似基督教咁做左羅馬國教，唐三藏取大乘佛法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中世紀就勁<br />\n現代衰落啦<br />\n至於基督徒話伊斯蘭用武力傳教<br />\n咁都要基督徒唔夠打先得<br />\n而伊斯蘭教徒在中世紀點解咁好打<br />\n就真係要深入研究先答到你<br />\n<br />\n可是我知道喺中世紀時伊斯蘭教徒控制嘅地方<br />\n異教徒同不信者只需要交多d稅<br />\n無記載話搞宗教審判所之類<br />\n相比當時歐洲，確實吸引到好多人材到中東<br />\n有巴打曾經提出佢睇過資料話中世紀耶路撒冷嘅猶太人長期被基督徒迫害<br />\n所以求回人打救佢<br />\n不過我google唔到有關資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_Golden_Age\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIslamic_Golden_Age&d=ziEEZpoG8a6kV4yLpptPHpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=29e64289\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_Golden_Age</a><br />\n<br />\n另外我個人認為可/古蘭經係基督教異端寫嘅亦都解答左不少反耶有神論者疑問<br />\n所以一推出市面<br />\n就迅即得到長期被迫害嘅異端同反耶有神論者支持<br />\n所以信徒可能因此迅速增長</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thejc.com/comment/comment/so-what-did-the-muslims-do-for-the-jews-1.33597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejc.com%2Fcomment%2Fcomment%2Fso-what-did-the-muslims-do-for-the-jews-1.33597&d=ziEEZpoG8a6kV4yLpptPHpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b534c862\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thejc.com/comment/comment/so-what-did-the-muslims-do-for-the-jews-1.33597</a><br />\nIslam saved Jewry. This is an unpopular, discomforting claim in the modern world. But it is a historical truth."},{"pid":"93aa831ad3b19c2b8cd3fafe21649397243b44a7","tid":422526,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然我都係無神論者不過都想知道點解咁多人信依啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信伊斯蘭教好多係「世襲」<br />\n即係老豆老母信，仔女就跟住信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e676b8d1553da3e8650d968860e5b4ac9957040","tid":422526,"uid":66340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"穆斯林=恐怖份子=地球垃圾"},{"pid":"0571985bc0e17b12acb75343e4dc250c55bb5d48","tid":422526,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雖然我都係無神論者不過都想知道點解咁多人信依啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信伊斯蘭教好多係「世襲」<br />\n即係老豆老母信，仔女就跟住信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慘"},{"pid":"bcb5b5285a01f1ad81e00765